---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Pete Ghiorse — AI product leader, founder, and builder.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Me</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-(--color-text-muted) leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I'm Pete Ghiorse — a product leader and founder who builds AI products that solve real problems for real people.
      </p>

      <p>
        Currently, I split my time between two roles: <strong class="text-(--color-text)">Senior PM for AI/ML at Capital One</strong>,
        where I lead ML-powered fraud and spend management at scale, and building
        <strong class="text-(--color-text)">Honeydew</strong>, an AI-powered family coordination app that uses voice, text,
        and photo input to keep families organized.
      </p>

      <p>
        Before that, I co-founded <strong class="text-(--color-text)">GiveTide</strong>, a fintech platform I grew from zero
        to a successful acquisition in 2022 over five years.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-(--color-text) pt-4">What I Care About</h2>

      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
        <li>Building AI systems that are genuinely useful, not just technically impressive</li>
        <li>The messy reality of shipping ML in production</li>
        <li>Agentic architectures and multi-tool orchestration</li>
        <li>Making families' lives less chaotic through technology</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-(--color-text) pt-4">Background</h2>

      <p>
        I studied <strong class="text-(--color-text)">Finance & Economics</strong> at the
        <strong class="text-(--color-text)">University of Richmond</strong>, graduating Magna Cum Laude.
        My career has spanned fintech, AI/ML, and consumer products — always at the intersection of
        technology and real-world impact.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-(--color-text) pt-4">Outside Work</h2>

      <p>
        <!-- TODO: Add personal interests, hobbies, etc. -->
        More coming soon.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
